[+++ b/docs/reference/setup.asciidoc, +, +[float], +[[jvm-version]], +== Java version, +, +Elasticsearch is built using Java, and requires at least, +http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html[Java 7] in, +order to run added[1.2.0,Was at least Java 6 before]. Only Oracle's Java and, +the OpenJDK are supported., +, +We recommend installing the *Java 8 update 20 or later*, or *Java 7 update 55, +or later*.  Previous versions of Java 7 are known to have bugs that can cause, +index corruption and data loss., +, +The version of Java to use can be configured by setting the `JAVA_HOME`, +environment variable., +]